Dino Melaye, a prominent Nigerian politician and former senator who represented the good people of Kogi West in the National Assembly, stirred outrage on social media after sharing a new video of himself inspecting his campaign office. Senator Dino Melaye posted the video to his verified Instagram account few hours ago.

In the video he shared yesterday on his Instagram page, the former senator can be seen moving from one office to another as he inspects the campaign office he built in Kabba, Kogi State. At the front of the campaign office, a Nigeria flag can be seen standing in between two PDP flags.
As the preparation for the 2023 general elections heightened, former Kogi West senator, Dino Melaye, has hinted that he be participating in an election soon as he said Dino is coming.
Speaking furthermore, while uploading the video on Instagram, Dino Melaye penned the following;
“Inspecting my campaign office in Kabba today….built and furnished by SDM. Dino is coming”
Many of his colleagues, fans and followers have reacted to the video he shared via liking and commenting underneath the post.
